<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LRT Density - About</title>
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    
    <style>
        /* Tailwind Configuration: 
        */
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                 extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'primary': 'var(--color-primary)', 
                        'secondary': 'var(--color-secondary)',
                        'accent': 'var(--color-accent)', 
                        'light-crowd': 'var(--crowd-light)',
                        'moderate-crowd': 'var(--crowd-moderate)',
                        'heavy-crowd': 'var(--crowd-heavy)',
                   },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                }
            }
           }
           
        /* Custom Card Styling */
        .content-card {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);   
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen pt-20 flex flex-col items-center">

    <header class="header-nav fixed w-full top-0"> 
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex justify-between items-center py-3">
            
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 flex-grow">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
                     <div class="h-6 w-6 bg-orange-500 rounded-md"></div>
                    <span class="text-xl font-extrabold text-orange-500">LRT</span>
                </div>

                <div class="relative flex items-center bg-gray-800 rounded-full px-4 py-2 max-w-sm w-full transition-all duration-300">
                    <i data-lucide="search" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-400 mr-2"></i>
                    <input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="SEARCH STATION" class="bg-transparent text-white placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none flex-grow text-sm">
                    <button id="clear-search" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" onclick="clearSearch()">
                        <i data-lucide="x" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                     </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <nav id="nav-links" class="flex items-center space-x-6">
                <a href="/" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">HOME</a>
                <a href="/about" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-black font-extrabold py-2 px-4 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hidden sm:block">ABOUT</a>
     
                {{#if user}}
                    <a href="/profile" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors hidden sm:block">PROFILE</a>
                    <a href="/logout" class="text-red-400 font-semibold hover:text-red-500 transition-colors hidden sm:block">LOG OUT</a>
                {{else}}
                    <a href="/login" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors hidden sm:block">LOG IN</a>
                    <a href="/register" class="text-white font-semibold hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors hidden sm:block">REGISTER</a>
                {{/if}}
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <main class="w-full max-w-5xl px-4 mt-8 space-y-10 mb-12">
        
        <header class="text-center pt-8 pb-4">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold text-white uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Our Mission</h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 font-medium">Empowering Commuters to Plan Proactively</p>
        </header>

        <section class="p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl content-card border border-gray-700/50">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">The Problem We Solve</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-bold text-white">Trains are regularly packed</span> during rush hours, leaving thousands of commuters unable to board, causing long delays and stress.
                Currently, there is <span class="text-heavy-crowd font-bold">no easy way</span> to check the current situation of a train platform without physically being there, turning a commute into a gamble.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl content-card border border-gray-700/50">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-accent mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Our Key Design Principles</h2>
            <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-200">
                
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
       
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1">
                        <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                    </div>
     
                    <p class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold text-white">Focus on Impossibility:</span> Our density metrics (Light, Moderate, Heavy) are calibrated to the user-defined threshold: the point where boarding becomes <span class="text-heavy-crowd font-bold">physically impossible</span>, not just uncomfortable.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1">
                        <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm-7-9.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L8 10.586l2.293-2.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L8 7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l3 3z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold text-white">Actionable Insight:</span> Commuters prefer <span class="text-heavy-crowd font-bold">simple color codes</span> (Green, Yellow, Red) for quick comprehension and actionable planning over raw data percentages.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 text-primary mt-1">
                        <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm-5-8a1 1 0 011-1h8a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H6a1 1 0 01-1-1v-2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-lg"><span class="font-bold text-white">Stress Reduction:</span> Providing this information reduces commuter stress and increases their sense of <span class="text-heavy-crowd font-bold">control</span> over their 
travel, enabling them to choose alternatives like delaying the trip or finding a different route.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="p-8 rounded-xl shadow-2xl content-card border border-gray-700/50">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 border-b border-gray-700 pb-2">Developed By</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300">This platform 
is developed by a team of students from De La Salle University, under the challenge-based learning, committed to finding innovative solutions for everyday world problems such as <span class="text-heavy-crowd font-bold">commuter challenges</span>.</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-1 text-lg text-gray-300 font-medium">
                <li>AKISHA JENEILLE C. AFRICA</li>
                <li>ED BENNETT L. BORROMEO</li>
                 <li>RIENZEL KRISTIAN P. GALANG</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

    </main>
    
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            // Initialize Lucide icons
            lucide.createIcons();

            // Search Bar Logic
            document.getElementById('search-input').addEventListener('keypress', function(e) {
                if (e.key === 'Enter' && this.value.trim() !== '') {
                    window.location.href = `/search?query=${encodeURIComponent(this.value.trim())}`;
                }
            });
        });

        function clearSearch() { 
            document.getElementById('search-input').value = ''; 
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>